title: Looking for team don't really care what rank you are
body:
looking to have some fun have a few wins see how we go, don't care what rank you are just as long as you are willing to learn from mistakes and do well in a team. I'm Gold 3 main adc and or mid add me in game if you wanna join or comment on here. If you add me in game send me a message so i know your interested.
COmmunication is required. Curse highly prefable

replies.body: Add me in game, we recently made a new team if you are interested send me a message in game
Add me to the team please :3
